## Key Difference from workshop-server

| Aspect | workshop-server | demo_cluster (this plan) |
|--------|-----------------|--------------------------|
| Architecture | HTTP server + REST API | Direct test binary |
| Pattern | Like a service | Like kms-flow-simulation |
| Execution | Server runs, clients call API | Run binary, flow executes |
| Session mgmt | SessionRegistry | Local variables |
| Use case | External clients | Internal testing |

